#: includes/security/class-gdpr-compliance.php:91
msgid "SwiftCurrency Multi-Currency"
msgstr "SwiftCurrency Multi-Moneda"

#: includes/security/class-gdpr-compliance.php:92
msgid "Our multi-currency plugin collects and stores certain data to provide currency conversion functionality."
msgstr "Nuestro plugin multi-moneda recopila y almacena ciertos datos para proporcionar funcionalidad de conversión de moneda."

#: includes/security/class-gdpr-compliance.php:93
msgid "What Data We Collect"
msgstr "Qué Datos Recopilamos"

#: includes/security/class-gdpr-compliance.php:94
msgid "Currency preferences: We store your selected currency in a cookie to remember your preference."
msgstr "Preferencias de moneda: Almacenamos su moneda seleccionada en una cookie para recordar su preferencia."

#: includes/security/class-gdpr-compliance.php:95
msgid "IP Address: We may use your IP address for geolocation to suggest a currency (anonymized if GDPR mode is enabled)."
msgstr "Dirección IP: Podemos usar su dirección IP para geolocalización para sugerir una moneda (anonimizada si el modo RGPD está habilitado)."

#: includes/security/class-gdpr-compliance.php:96
msgid "Order currency: We store which currency was used for each order."
msgstr "Moneda del pedido: Almacenamos qué moneda se utilizó para cada pedido."

#: includes/security/class-gdpr-compliance.php:97
msgid "How Long We Keep Your Data"
msgstr "Cuánto Tiempo Conservamos Sus Datos"

#: includes/security/class-gdpr-compliance.php:98
msgid "Currency preference cookies are stored for 30 days. Order currency data is kept as long as the order exists. IP addresses are anonymized immediately if GDPR mode is enabled."
msgstr "Las cookies de preferencia de moneda se almacenan durante 30 días. Los datos de moneda del pedido se conservan mientras exista el pedido. Las direcciones IP se anonimizan inmediatamente si el modo RGPD está habilitado."

#: includes/security/class-gdpr-compliance.php:99
msgid "Your Rights"
msgstr "Sus Derechos"

#: includes/security/class-gdpr-compliance.php:100
msgid "You can request to export or delete your currency preference data at any time. Contact us to exercise your rights."
msgstr "Puede solicitar exportar o eliminar sus datos de preferencia de moneda en cualquier momento. Contáctenos para ejercer sus derechos."

#: includes/security/class-gdpr-compliance.php:112
msgid "SwiftCurrency Data"
msgstr "Datos de SwiftCurrency"

#: includes/security/class-gdpr-compliance.php:145
msgid "Currency Preferences"
msgstr "Preferencias de Moneda"

#: includes/security/class-gdpr-compliance.php:149
msgid "Preferred Currency"
msgstr "Moneda Preferida"

